{{!
    @template mod_booking/form-course-selector-suggestion

    Moodle template for the list of valid options in an autocomplate form element.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id int course id
    * shortname string short name of the course
    * fullname string name of the course

    Example context (json):
    {
        "id" : 12,
        "shortname" : "courseshortname",
        "fullname" : "Full name of the course"
    }
}}
<span class="course-suggestion font-weight-bold">
    {{fullname}} (ID: {{id}})<br>
    <small>{{shortname}}</small>
</span>
